<div class="clearfix" id="welcomeContent">
	<div id="gravatarContainer">
    <img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/<%= gravatar_self %>?s=70&d=mm" class="homepage_gravatar" />
  </div>
  <div id="welcomeMessage">
    <h1>Messageboard Home</h1>
    <h2>Welcome, <%= @user.username %>!
    <% if is_admin %>
      Congratulations, you have been promoted to Administrator!
    <% end %>
    </h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="welcomeText">
	<p>Welcome to BME.</p>
	<p>If you don't have an avatar image, head over to <%= link_to 'gravatar.com', 'http://www.gravatar.com' %> and signup. There currently is no other custom avatar functionality.</p>
	
	<p>I'm building this thing from scratch, on my own, so if there's a problem either <%= link_to 'email me', 'mailto:bryanmytko@gmail.com' %> or shut up. Eventually there will be a lot of a features, and it will be a lot more ~social, but for now it's just a simple messageboard.</p>
	
	<p><strong>Known issues &amp; missing features include:</strong> <s>no link parsing</s>, <s>no image uploading</s>, <s>no topic creation</s>, no post editing, incomplete user pages, no pagination, as well as a bunch of other things. This is barely considered an alpha release, but I want to build some interest so feel free to get involved. And, if you'd really like to get involved and you're into <%= link_to 'this sort of thing','http://i.imgur.com/VhlQK.gif' %>, the source is here: <%= link_to 'https://github.com/bryanmytko/mboard', 'https://github.com/bryanmytko/mboard' %> - Feel free to contribute, fork, whatever.</p>
	
	<p>Also, don't do anything stupid or I <em>will</em> ban you.</p>
</div>

<div id="topics" class="clearfix">
	<table cellpadding="0" cellmargin="0">
		<tr>
			<th class="title">
				Topic
			</th>
			<th>
				Replies
			</th>
			<th>
				Last Reply By?
			</th>
			<th>
				Views
			</th>
			<th>
				Last Post
			</th>
		</tr>
	<% @topics.each do |t| %>
	<tr>
		<td class="title">
	    <%= link_to t.title.capitalize, topic_path(t.slug) %>
	  </td>
	  <td>
		  <p><%= reply_count(t.id) %></p>
		</td>
		<td>
			<p><%= unless (t.last_author).nil?
				  link_to t.last_author, user_path(t.last_author)
				else
				  '-'
				end
			%></p>
		</td>
		<td>
			<p><%= t.view_count.to_s %></p>
		</td>
	  <td>
		  <p><%= t.updated_at.to_formatted_s(:long_ordinal) %>
				<% if is_admin %>
				  <%= link_to '[X]', remove_topic_path(t), :confirm => "Are you sure?", :class => 'delete_button' %>
				<% end %>
			</p>
	  </td>
	</tr>
	<% end %>
  
  <tr id="newTopic">
	  <td colspan="6">
	    <%= form_for @topic do |t| %>
	    <%= t.label :title, "New Topic: " %>
	    <%= t.text_field :title %>
	    <%= t.submit "Create!" %>
	    <% end %>
	  </td>
  </tr>

	</table>
</div>